videos.headline: Erdely finds Ubosi for 38-yard UAB TD
videos.description: A.J. Erdely pinpoints Xavier Ubosi with a 38-yard touchdown pass to give UAB the 7-0 lead over Rice.

videos.headline: UAB recovers blocked punt in end zone
videos.description: UAB comes up with a big blocked punt and recovers the ball in the end zone for a touchdown.

videos.headline: Erdely sprints 19 yards for UAB TD
videos.description: A.J. Erdely takes off for 19 yards through the Rice defense for the touchdown putting the Blazers up over the Owls 28-0.

videos.headline: Street fights for 2-yard TD for UAB
videos.description: Jarrior Street powers through the Owls defense for the touchdown putting UAB up 35-0

videos.headline: Brown slides through for another UAB rushing TD
videos.description: Spencer Brown takes the handoff and slips through the Rice defense for the touchdown putting UAB on top of Rice 42-0.
